Paper: hep-th/0206096

Date: 2002-06-12

Title: Entropy of the Stiffest Stars

Authors: T.Banks, W.Fischler, A.Kashani-Poor, R.McNees, S.Paban

Comments: 16 pages, 5 figures

Journal-ref: Class.Quant.Grav. 19 (2002) 4717-4728

We analyze the properties of stars whose interior is described by thestiffest equation of state consistent with causality. We note the remarkablefact that the entropy of such stars scales like the area.